12c3b4eb96fd4309db80db9bfc772ea4f81898bf98e530975c967a949d20fb0f9f4468bf98b78fbdc56cc9b83f5737991bed06552ef679b7c7cc3856a4b340a9  0100-Revert-tail-fix-detection-of-closed-stdout-on-macOS.patch
